122
00:06:44,290 --> 00:06:45,340
(And Long Mengli's
Dreamfinder Clothing Store)

123
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:46,520
(opens its 100th branch,)

124
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,700
(becoming a renowned premier tailor.)

